    severity: 'high',
    category: 'Financial Crimes',
    date: 'August 20, 2020',
    lastUpdated: 'February 8, 2026',
    summary: 'Steve Bannon, Brian Kolfage, and others defrauded donors of millions through the "We Build the Wall" crowdfunding campaign that raised $25 million. Bannon was indicted but pardoned by Trump on his last day in office. Kolfage was sentenced to 51 months in federal prison. The scheme used wall-building as a cover for personal enrichment.',
