      'GIULIANI VERDICT: Rudy Giuliani was separately found liable for defaming Georgia election workers Ruby Freeman and Shaye Moss with similar false claims. A jury ordered him to pay $148 million. He filed for bankruptcy.',
      'SMARTMATIC CASE: Another voting machine company, Smartmatic, has a $2.7 billion lawsuit against Fox still pending. The case could produce another massive judgment.',
