      'NY ATTORNEY GENERAL LAWSUIT: New York AG Letitia James sued to dissolve the NRA, documenting over $64 million in waste and self-dealing. The lawsuit alleged LaPierre and other executives violated nonprofit law and their fiduciary duties.',
