      'PRICE STOCK TRADING: Before becoming HHS Secretary, Price traded healthcare stocks while legislating healthcare policy. He purchased shares in a medical device company days before introducing legislation benefiting that company.',
      'SCOTT PRUITT - EPA CORRUPTION: EPA Administrator Scott Pruitt faced at least 18 federal investigations into his conduct. He built a $43,000 soundproof phone booth in his office, flew first class claiming security threats, and had aides do personal errands.',
