      'BARR AS ENABLER: William Barr misrepresented the Mueller report before its release, claiming it exonerated Trump. He intervened in cases involving Trump allies Roger Stone and Michael Flynn to reduce consequences.',
      'STONE SENTENCING: Career prosecutors recommended 7-9 years for Roger Stone. After Trump tweeted criticism, DOJ leadership intervened to request less. The prosecutors withdrew from the case in protest.',
