      'SAM SALEHPOUR: Current Boeing engineer speaking out about 787 Dreamliner production defects. He reports gaps between fuselage sections that could cause fatigue and failure. Boeing has disputed his claims. He continues to speak.',
      'THE PATTERN: Raise concerns → Be ignored → Retaliation → Concerns proven correct by death → Boeing pays fine → No executive jailed → Next whistleblower → Repeat.',
